        <div class="row mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto">
                <h6>Our Services</h6>
                <p class="mb-0">At Megway Parcels, we offer a wide array of services designed to meet all your shipping and business needs. Our goal is to provide comprehensive solutions that save you time and money while ensuring your items are delivered safely and on time.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Parcel Delivery Services:</b> We provide fast and secure parcel delivery both within the UK and internationally. Our partnerships with multiple couriers allow us to offer you the best rates in town, making sure your parcels reach their destination safely and on time. Whether you're sending a small package or a large shipment, we have the right solution for you. Our advanced tracking system allows you to monitor your parcel's journey from start to finish, giving you peace of mind and ensuring your items are always in good hands.</li>
                    <li><b>Mailbox Rentals:</b> Secure a personal or business mailbox at our store. Starting from just £10 a month, our mailboxes provide a safe and reliable address for receiving your mail and packages. This service is perfect for individuals who need a secure place to receive their mail, as well as businesses looking for a professional mailing address. Our mailboxes are accessible during our convenient store hours, and we offer flexible rental terms to suit your needs.</li>
                    <li><b>Packaging Supplies:</b> We stock a variety of packaging supplies, including cardboard boxes of all sizes, mail bags, envelopes, and various types of tapes. Everything you need to pack your items securely can be found here. Our knowledgeable staff can help you choose the right packaging materials to ensure your items are protected during transit. We also offer custom packaging solutions for unique or fragile items, providing an extra layer of security and peace of mind.</li>
                    <li><b>Drop-Off Points:</b> We serve as a convenient drop-off point for major couriers, including Royal Mail, EVRI, DPD, DHL, FedEx, and Amazon Locker. Just drop your parcels with us, and we’ll handle the rest. This service is designed to save you time and make shipping easier, whether you're sending a single package or multiple shipments. Our friendly staff is always on hand to assist you with any questions or special requests, ensuring your parcels are processed quickly and efficiently.</li>
                    <li><b>Business Services:</b> Enhance your business with our document scanning and printing services. We also design and print posters, flyers, leaflets, and business cards, helping your business stand out. Our professional-grade equipment and high-quality materials ensure your printed materials look sharp and professional. Whether you need a small batch of business cards or a large run of promotional flyers, we can handle it all. Our design team is available to help you create eye-catching and effective marketing materials that reflect your brand and attract customers.</li>

                </ul>
            </div>
